Great.  The service, food and atmosphere were great.   Asparagus and lobster soup.  Prosciutto wrapped pork tenderloin.  Wow.   We'll be back.

Jon was a wonderful server - very attentive and kind. Their signature dish is what I ordered; carlesimo - a must order. It was delicious. The bread was amazing and the tiramisu was some of the best I've ever had. Bravo to the cooks for some amazing, true Italian food!

Osteria needs to be on everyone's Go To list.  Their high-end Italian food is matched with great service.  Excellent for date night or meeting friends for a relaxing dinner. There is also a bar that serves full menu.  If you want spaghetti and meatballs, go somewhere else.

AL and his Team created a spectacular evening 'Family Style' for our party of 9. Memorable from the Antipasto and Ciopino thru the Veal Saltimboca and See Bass thru the Tiramisu and housemate Gelato. Server Michael and runners waited on our group very attentively and did not miss a beat. Great yourself to a memory at Osteria! 👏🎉👍
